{"type": "article", "id": 38926, "title": "春天要来了，在家里也可以赏花了｜这个设计了不起", "description": "每个周末，《好奇心日报》都会找个主题为你寻找精彩设计。", "date": "2017-03-17T23:41:55Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 38653, "name": "bande"}, {"id": 38654, "name": "100%"}, {"id": 38655, "name": "Sun-Star"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 241, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170317230329qdRrSHL8vctNhBXx.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #323333} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><p class=\"\">天气逐渐变暖，你是否正准备着踏青赏花呢？如果你想避免舟车劳顿或者人山人海，不妨看看这些可以让你在家就能轻松赏花的设计。</p><h3>Sakurasaku by 100%</h3><p>水渍变好看了之后，你还舍得把它们擦掉吗？设计公司 100% 创作的这套玻璃杯有着樱花造型的杯底，可以像印章那样留下一枚樱花的轮廓。既然主打的是樱花的概念，除了透明的杯子之外，它还有淡粉色和模拟雪樱的毛玻璃款。你可以通过 100% 的<a href=\"https://100percent.stores.jp/\">官方网站</a>购买，单只售价从 2484 日元起，有清酒杯、啤酒杯和威士忌杯等多个款式。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170317230911ByU1l4dFAJ39EbiG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.634375\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170317230911vMq5xtEOwi8zpm73.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.634375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170317230911WwntLZl8BmCzx4r0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170317230911yS5w4smut10LIV3M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.634375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Sakura pencil by Sun-Star</h3><p>自 1995 年起，日本文具公司 Sun-Star 每年都会举办一届文具设计比赛，帮助有趣的概念变为实体，这支能削出樱花花瓣的铅笔就是 2015 年的获奖作品。在设计师<a href=\"http://www.sun-star-st.jp/campaign/standard_stationery/sakurasaku_pencil/20th_p_a11.html\">土居裕彰</a>看来，一年级新生用小手握住铅笔第一次写下文字、再不断将笔尖削尖的过程，完全可以与稍纵即逝的樱花联系在一起：入学刚好是一年一度的樱花季，而飘落的花瓣则象征着孩子的成长。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.jp/%E3%81%95%E3%81%8F%E3%82%89%E3%81%95%E3%81%8F%E3%81%88%E3%82%93%E3%81%B4%E3%81%A4-PP-S5007984-%E3%82%BD%E3%83%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%A8%E3%82%B7%E3%83%8E-%E3%82%B5%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B9%E3%82%BF%E3%83%BC%E6%96%87%E5%85%B7/dp/B01MCW8SHY\">购买链接</a>，售价为 1272 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170317230850f1PdGs9EehFUzxow.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666154\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170317230850qw3i6zAFLQkXZCsR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.096923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170317230851iK3Gqb8hapO6rRez.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.616923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170317230851u7HvoZGMND4QlW6O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.900000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170317230850kolvw4Tq3hFIKBCb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.206154\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Flowerium by Rie Okitsu</h3><p>来自日本的 Rie Okitsu 是一名医学研究员，热爱花卉的她希望从自己的专业角度出发，探索花艺的另一种表达可能。基于这个理念，她创立了名为 Flowerium 的花艺工作室，将回收来的废弃灯泡作为盛放花朵的容器，和其它标本相比，多了一份生活气息。美中不足的是，<a href=\"http://flowerium.jp/\">Flowerium</a> 的产品目前只能从实体店购买，官网的商店还在筹备当中。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170317231254GIiCD8WARx0QrNp5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664615\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170317231254JK8nICo9yua5Bt3H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170317231254LHqjox7bTpOvengZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666154\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703172312556SaWN7Rq5s0cmbEg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.770769\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Masking Roll Sticker by bande</h3><p>Masking Roll Sticker 是和纸胶带品牌 bande 所推出的变体胶带系列，和其它常见和纸胶带不同的单片式设计让它们看起来就像是一长串组合在一起的粘纸，使用起来更加灵活。最近，bande 就配合季节变化推出了花瓣造型的胶带，只要细心观察就能发现每一片花瓣在深浅和大小上都有着细微的差别。你可以通过 bande 的<a href=\"https://bande.ne.jp/?mode=cate&amp;cbid=2238102&amp;csid=0\">官方网站</a>购买，售价为 432 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170317230835Rnje8SDmLgxcqpOU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750769\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170317230836VYzH3er5EMX2KJLk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750769\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170317230835pejOkoYKwAUWMXc7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.970769\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703172308359OlfSTX8KvdwN21Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750769\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Sakura Jelly by Eitaro</h3><p>在日本，赏樱季的到来意味着不少“季节限定”版和菓子也将陆续登场。这款樱花果冻就是拥有百年历史的和菓子老铺荣太楼的春季看板，盐渍的樱花在加入甜烈酒的淡粉色果冻中自然地舒展、定格，让人不忍心吃掉。有了造型和口味的双重加持，推出至今已有十多年的它仍保持着相当高的人气，去年还创下了 25 万盒的销售记录。如果你感兴趣的话，可以通过荣太楼的<a href=\"http://shop.eitaro.net/products/list.php?category_id=44\">官方网站</a>购买，单个售价为 250 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170317230401MQYsDBqE29IlHio1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667241\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170317230400aICid6Xw10vRpoDZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667241\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170317230401M43xqdyVPTOnl50t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667241\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170317230400G8YckKbFA1jThSM2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>T tea packaging by Maria Milagros Rodriguez Bouroncle</h3><p>如果打开茶包的过程就像是一朵花的绽放，你会更愿意喝茶吗？这款名为 T 的概念包装是法国设计师 Maria Milagros Rodriguez Bouroncle 的作品，7 种茶叶被装在不同颜色的纸盒中，展开后盒子本身又变身为带着一小段根茎的花朵，便于浸泡。享用完热茶，纸片还可以收集起来作为装饰。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017031723292213EiyogIkZvPTxq2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.520000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170317232922GLNtPud1MWxvyboC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.718750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170317232921GEQdbY7OPAFweHJI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.852500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170317232921y8RULCWF4MKj1BaX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.013750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}